{"tid":2073121,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"開始咗實習嘅 分享吓你哋學咗乜","createTime":"2020-06-21T05:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T04:17:43.000Z","uid":148551,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3d56c7a196ec318735ab873dcb4d35fdc1cc30","tid":2073121,"uid":148551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:43:57.000Z","msg":"做咗兩個星期實習<br />\n同我想像中有啲分別 唔係hea<br />\n唔知係咪得閒得滯 同埋我鍾意吹水<br />\n本身兩個supervisors 負責睇我<br />\n吹吹下<br />\n結果成條Team 5個Engineers 都得閒走來教我哋嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲阿Sir仲要好好人 一個會約我lunch去問書<br />\n一個幫我擋左paper works 自己去scan 野 叫我去學program<br />\n一個唔介意我唔記得晒啲嘢 全部重溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以開始左兩個星期真係對成個行業熟悉咗好多 同埋知道咗邊啲野係有用 所以某程度上有啲驚訝 同我想像中有啲分別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想知道有冇其他實習緊嘅巴打都有啲真係學到野嘅經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6975afc33c7af974b4aa203541beb8a367c3d113","tid":2073121,"uid":38904,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"只係你好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1efc92f7b775f06fe7ed19d18fac5ca58e3b435","tid":2073121,"uid":167464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"睇tender睇COP睇technical specification，幫手做purchasing ，幫手填form畀政府，畫cad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694f470aaaf5b9fa68e9ec967569cb04cd317b0d","tid":2073121,"uid":80866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6975afc33c7af974b4aa203541beb8a367c3d113","tid":2073121,"uid":38904,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"只係你好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"a6f681f136ba79c9c8e0608c08f6656e3fd6f701","tid":2073121